在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''菱形六十面體'''是一種[[星形菱形三十面體|星形菱形三十面體]]，由赫爾穆特·溫克爾巴赫（Helmut Unkelbach）於1940年發現<ref>{{Cite journal | author = Unkelbach, Helmut | title = "Die kantensymmetrischen, gleichkantigen Polyeder." | journal= Deutsche Math. | volume= 5 | pages= 306-316 | year= 1940 }}</ref>，因此又稱為'''溫克爾巴赫六十面體'''（Unkelbach's hexecontahedron）<ref>{{cite web|author=Branko Grünbaum|url=https://digital.lib.washington.edu/researchworks/bitstream/handle/1773/15593/Bilinski_dodecahedron.pdf|title=The Bilinski dodecahedron, and assorted parallelohedra, zonohedra, monohedra, isozonohedra and otherhedra.|publisher=lib.washington.edu|accessdate=2020-08-20|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055021/https://digital.lib.washington.edu/researchworks/bitstream/handle/1773/15593/Bilinski_dodecahedron.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這個星形多面體由60個[[黃金菱形|黃金菱形]]以非凸的方式依照二十面體對稱性構成，共有60個面、120條稜和62個頂點。<ref name="Kabai, Sándor 2002">{{Cite book | author = Kabai, Sándor | title = "Mathematical Graphics I: Lessons in Computer Graphics Using Mathematica." | location= Püspökladány, Hungary | publisher= Uniconstant | pages= pp. 171, 179, 181 | year= 2002 }}</ref>此外，{{化學式|鋁|6|鋰|3|銅}}之準晶體聚集體的核在緩慢結晶的情況下會形成菱形六十面體的形狀<ref name="article guyot1987news">{{cite journal
  |title=News on five-fold symmetry
  |author=Guyot, P
  |journal=Nature
  |volume=326
  |number=6114
  |pages=pp.640-641
  |year=1987
  |publisher=Nature Publishing Group}}</ref>。

菱形六十面體與鳶形六十面體拓樸同構，其差異在於菱形六十面體面是菱形，而鳶形六十面體的面是鳶形。

== 歷史 ==
菱形六十面體這種幾何結構最早由赫爾穆特·溫克爾巴赫（Helmut Unkelbach）於1940年發現，並做出了觀察及描繪。然而關於與這種形狀相似的分析與討論可能早在1619年就已經出現了<ref name="article kabai2011inside"/>。1619年克普勒在其撰寫的書Harmonies of the World中對菱形三十面體進行了分析與討論<ref>{{cite book | author = Johannes Kepler | title = Harmonices Mundi | publisher = Linz | year = 1619 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/five-cube-intersection.html | title = The Intersection of the Five Cubes | author = George W. Hart | publisher = Virtual Polyhedra | year = 1996 | accessdate = 2020-08-20 | archive-date = 2019-12-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191230064616/http://georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/five-cube-intersection.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，其中探討到了部分變體與菱形六十面體類似<ref name="article kabai2011inside">{{cite journal
  |url=https://archive.bridgesmathart.org/2011/bridges2011-387.pdf
  |title=Inside and Outside the Rhombic Hexecontahedron
  |author=Kabai, Sándor,
  |journal=Proceedings of Bridges 2011
  |pages=387--394
  |year=2011
  |access-date=2020-08-20
  |archive-date=2020-08-24
  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824122402/https://archive.bridgesmathart.org/2011/bridges2011-387.pdf
  |dead-url=no
  }}</ref>。1984年D. Shechtman等人發現了一種五重對稱性的準晶體結構
<ref name=s>{{cite journal |last1=Shechtman |first1=D. |last2=Blech |first2=I. |last3=Gratias |first3=D. |last4=Cahn |first4=J. |year=1984 |title=Metallic Phase with Long-Range Orientational Order and No Translational Symmetry|journal=Physical Review Letters |volume=53 |issue=20 |pages=1951–1953 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.53.1951 |bibcode=1984PhRvL..53.1951S}}</ref>，被認為與菱形六十面體十分接近<ref name="Á. Csanády">{{cite journal
  |title=hemical behaviour of the crystalline and quasicrystalline phases of aluminium alloys
  |author=Á. Csanády, V. Stefániay, A. Griger, L. Tomcsányi, B. Albert,
  |journal=Proceedings of the 8th ILMC
  |volume=22/23
  |number=6
  |pages=486
  |year=1987}}</ref><ref name="article doi:10.1080/13642818808211230">{{cite journal
|author = H.-U. Nissen, R. Wessicken, C. Beeli, Á. Csanády
|title = Al-Mn quasicrystal aggregates with icosahedral morphological symmetry
|journal = Philosophical Magazine B
|volume = 57
|number = 5
|pages = 587
|year  = 1988
|publisher = Taylor & Francis
|doi = 10.1080/13642818808211230}}</ref>，1986年這項發現被Guyot發表在[[自然_(期刊)|《自然》]]上<ref name="article guyot1987news"/>。

== 性質 ==
在不考慮面自相交的情況下，這種立體是一種[[六十面體|六十面體]]<ref name="mathworld Hexecontahedron">{{mathworld | urlname = Hexecontahedron| title = Hexecontahedron}}</ref>，共有60個面、120條稜和62個頂點。<ref name="Kabai, Sándor 2002"/>。然而若作為菱形三十面體的星形化體，則其是由30個自相交的多邊形構成。這種結構可以透過直接將菱形三十面體的面延伸來構成，如[[:File:Construction_of_Rhombic_hexecontahedron_from_Rhombic_Triacontahedron.gif|動畫]]所示。<ref name="Kabai, Sándor 2002"/>
