菱形六十面體是[[Wolfram_Alpha|Wolfram Alpha]]的[[标志|标志]]上所呈現的形狀<ref group="lower-roman">{{Cite web | url=https://blog.wolframalpha.com/2009/05/19/whats-in-the-logo-that-which-we-call-a-rhombic-hexecontahedron | author=Weisstein, E. W | title="What's In a Name? That Which We Call a Rhombic Hexecontahedron." | date=2009-05-19 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215120750/http://blog.wolframalpha.com/2009/05/19/whats-in-the-logo-that-which-we-call-a-rhombic-hexecontahedron/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[沃尔夫勒姆研究公司|沃尔夫勒姆研究公司]]中被稱為「spikey」<ref group="lower-roman">{{Cite web | url=https://writings.stephenwolfram.com/2018/12/the-story-of-spikey/ | author=Weisstein, E. W | title="the-story-of-spikey" | date=2018-12-28 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718142655/https://writings.stephenwolfram.com/2018/12/the-story-of-spikey/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在巴西的文化中，有一種有色織物和紙板製成的菱形六十面體狀手工藝品，稱為幸福之心（happiness stars，或稱giramundos，葡萄牙語world turners）。這種手工藝品一般由母親縫製並作為送給女兒的結婚禮物。直到20世紀上半葉，巴西農村學校仍在教授手工藝的技術。然而由於近年來都市化的關係，這種習俗與工藝逐漸失傳<ref name="Giramundos">{{Citation | url = https://impa.br/en_US/page-noticias/artesanato-se-antecipou-a-descoberta-de-poliedro-rombico | title = Artesanato se antecipou à descoberta de poliedro | publisher = [[Instituto_Nacional_de_Matemática_Pura_e_Aplicada|IMPA]] | accessdate = 2019-01-08 | trans-title = Handicraft-anticipated discovery of polyhedra | language = pt | archive-date = 2019-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190109204837/https://impa.br/en_US/page-noticias/artesanato-se-antecipou-a-descoberta-de-poliedro-rombico/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

